{{Infobox waterfall | name = Oliyarik Waterfalls | alt_name = ഓലിയരിക് വെള്ളച്ചാട്ടം | photo = | photo_width = | photo_caption = | location = [[Kollam District]], [[Kerala]], [[India]] | coordinates = | elevation = <!--- {{convert|80|m|abbr=on}} ---> | type = Segmented | height = <!--- {{convert|18|m|abbr=on}} ---> | width = <!--- {{convert|54|m|abbr=on}} ---> | height_longest = | average_width = | number_drops = | average_flow = <!--- 52 m<sup>3</sup>/s (1010 cu ft/s)---> | watercourse = [[Kallada River]] | world_rank = }} '''Oliyarik Waterfalls''' is a waterfall situated near [[Anchal]] in [[Kollam district]], India.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.mathrubhumi.com/travel/travel-news/onam-special-crowds-throng-the-virgin-oliyarik-waterfalls-english-news-1.1358217 |title=Onam special; Crowds throng the Virgin Oliyarik waterfalls |publisher=Mathrubhumi Daily |date=16 September 2016 |accessdate=8 December 2016}}</ref> It is the less known one among the four waterfalls in Kollam district. The falls is about 55&nbsp;km away from [[Kollam]] city.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://huntnews.in/p/detail/2619901457402871?uc_param_str=dnfrpfbivesscpgimibtbmntnijblauputoggdnw&pos=1474104027119&channel=travel&chncat=category_english |title=Onam special; Crowds throng the Virgin Oliyarik waterfalls |publisher=Hunt News |date= |accessdate=8 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mathrubhumi.com/travel/oliyarik-waterfall-1.1358244 |title=A snap of Oliyarik waterfalls |publisher=Mathrubhumi Daily |date= |accessdate=8 December 2016}}</ref>
