[[El Salvador]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/CE_ELSA.html</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle_registration_plates_of_the_United_States#Designs_and_serial_formats|North American standard]] 6 × 12 inches (152 × 300 mm).<ref>http://www.plateshack.com/y2k/El_Salvador/elsalvy2k.html</ref>
